condition.narrative: a) Schedule 2 Section I.A.2(b)(i) of the Loan Agreement: The Borrower shall appoint or hire as relevant, and maintain with suchqualifications and under terms of reference acceptable to the Bank within the PIU, one environmental specialist, one socialdevelopment specialist, and one gender-based violence specialist within sixty (60) days after the Effective Date.

b) Schedule 2 Section I.A.2(b)(ii) of the Loan Agreement: The Borrower shall appoint or hire as relevant, and maintain with suchqualifications and under terms of reference acceptable to the Bank in each municipality where Project activities are taking place,an environmental and social focal point within ninety (90) days after the Effective Date.

c) Schedule 2 Section I.A.2(b)(ii) of the Loan Agreement: The Borrower shall appoint or hire as relevant, and maintain with suchqualifications and under terms of reference acceptable to the Bank in each of the six (6) groups of provinces, an environmental andsocial specialist within ninety (90) days after the Effective Date.

d) Schedule 2 Section I.A.4(a) of the Loan Agreement, The Recipient shall within thirty (30) days after the Effective Dateestablish and maintain throughout Project implementation a Project Steering Committee (“PSC”) to provide overall strategic guidanceand coordination for the Project.
